# Tool Docstring Convention

glob pattern(s) for applicable files: services/analyst/tools/*.py, services/common/lib/tools/*.py, services/common/lib/integrations/connectors/saas/*/template.py

First line must be **concise but informative** - add value beyond the tool name. Don't just repeat what the name already says.

## Examples
- ✅ `Execute Python code and return stdout.`
- ✅ `List accounts with health scores using OData queries.`
- ✅ `Get a record by ID with optional associations.`
- ❌ `List HubSpot contacts.` (just repeats the tool name HUBSPOT_LIST_CONTACTS)
- ❌ `Run Python for ML, statistics, or transformations...` (describes use cases, not mechanics)
